      "text": "すずは振り付けの練習をしていた時から\n彼女達の曲を気に入っていたみたいだな",
      "startTime": 14.7854802404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、みなさんの楽しそうな演奏を聴いていると\nこちらまで幸せな気分になるのですわ！",
      "startTime": 21.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_07_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "放課後ティータイムは、聴く側も演奏する側も\nみんなが笑顔になる素晴らしいバンドですわね",
      "startTime": 29.4794184174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
